 scale and rotation.  \n- Test inputs to see virtual objects in different states.\n- Use demo objects to explore what\u2019s possible. ", "short_description": "Use Meta Spark Player to see your virtual objects come to life.\n\nThe virtual objects you create in Meta Spark Studio can be sent directly to Meta Spark Player. See and interact with your virtual objects in your surroundings using Passthrough on your Meta Quest device.  "}]}, "developer_name": "Meta Platforms, Inc", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.facebook.com/about/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://sparkar.facebook.com/ar-studio/terms/", "publisher_name": "Meta Platforms, Inc", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sparkar.facebook.com/ar-studio/", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "323450648956687"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ART_CREATIVITY", "SIMULATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "SITTING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "783066696356143"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75295751_952423296149544_6248543502049458911_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=hEulRPujPnEQ7kNvgGLHm0q&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD6nQF83OMcxbrftto9M1FXJrk6m3q2xlNaC5cVJnuS_Q&oe=6718DA96"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "Meta Spark Player", "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "context_category": null